                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc form="codex">
                            <supportDesc material="perg">
                                <support>
                                    <p>
                                        <material>Parchment</material>.</p>
                                </support>
                                <extent>2 leaves. Fol. 1 measures <dimensions scope="range" type="leaf">
                                        <height>268-272</height>
                                        <width>185-193</width>
                                    </dimensions>, fol. 2 measures <dimensions scope="range" type="leaf">
                                        <height>265-269</height>
                                        <width>193</width>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </extent>
                                <collation>The two leaves are conjoint.</collation>
                                <condition>
                                    <!-- Den ydre margen er næsten skåret væk og en snip af bladenes
                                        yderste hjørne, både foroven og forneden, er klippet bort;
                                        der er dog ikke sket teksttab, undtagen i de fem øverste
                                        linjer i den ydre spalte på bl. 1 (delvis ved hensmuldring),
                                        hvor der mangler ca. 9 mm. af linjerne, og i de øverstetre
                                        linjer i den ydre spalte på bl. 2, hvor der mangler ca. en
                                        tredjedel af linjerne. Der synes at være syhuller i ryggen -->
                                    <p>The outer margin is almost cut away and the upper and lower
                                        corner has been ploughed, yet it has not caused a loss of
                                        text except from on f. 1, partly by mouldering and the upper 3
                                        lines on the outer column on f. 2 where 1/3 of the lines are
                                        missing.</p>
                                </condition>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout columns="2" writtenLines="40">
                                    <p>The leaves are written in two columns with 40 lines per
                                        column, the size of the columns are approx. <dimensions
                                            scope="all" type="written">
                                            <height>218</height>
                                            <width>75-80</width>
                                        </dimensions>. Spaces on 3 lines are left empty for
                                        majuscules, except from a Þ containing a face on f. 2rb that
                                        later has been drawn in.</p>
                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <handDesc>
